sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Registry (ghcr.io/opensource-distroless)
    participant S as Source (Node.js LTS)
    participant GH as GitHub Action (Node Assembler)
    participant Sec as Security (Cosign/Trivy)
    
    GH->>R: Pull `cc:latest`
    R-->>GH: Download verified Opensource Distroless foundation
    GH->>Sec: `cosign verify` cc:latest ancestry
    Sec-->>GH: Pass
    
    GH->>S: curl node-v20.tar.gz
    S-->>GH: JavaScript Application Payload
    GH->>Sec: Confirm sha256 checksums match Node release
    
    GH->>GH: `FROM cc:latest` \n Overlay JRE into `/usr/local/lib/nodejs`
    
    GH->>Sec: `trivy image` Final Output Container
    Sec-->>GH: Pass (0 CRITICAL/HIGH CVEs)
    
    GH->>R: Push Execution Container (nodejs:latest)
    GH->>Sec: `cosign sign` Final OCI Manifest
